summary: The Indian Air Force has enhanced its arsenal of fighter aircraft with the introduction of Rampage long-range supersonic air-to-ground missiles, capable of striking targets up to 250 kilometers away. summary: The Supreme Court requested responses from the Centre, Punjab, and Haryana governments on a plea to establish the minimum support price (MSP), which includes periodic increases for alternative crops cultivated by farmers and their procurement by the government.
